# RVL_Augmentation

## What is this?

This is a sub project from the Ryerson Vision Lab to implement the augmentations layed out by http://arxiv.org/abs/1504.06852.

## Convention

Every augmentation added must supply a test (with asserts, but not necessarily an testing framework), which tests the transformation in question.

Every augmentation added must supply a check (visualiztion), whichs demonstrates that the augmentation in question does indeed work.
